# Bit of a naive test, but it found one bug, and is
# also a great example why nobody wants to program in this language!
# Doesn't test input or output. Outputs -1 on failure.

# Test ADD
LDA TWELVE
ADD TWENTY
SUB THIRTYTWO
BRZ TESTSUB
BRA ERR

# Test SUB
TESTSUB LDA TWENTY
SUB TWELVE
SUB EIGHT
BRZ TESTSTALDA
BRA ERR

# Test STA and LDA
TESTSTALDA LDA TWENTY
STA PLACE
LDA PLACE
SUB TWENTY
BRZ TESTBRA
BRA ERR

# Test BRA
TESTBRA BRA TESTBRZ
BRA ERR

# Test BRZ
TESTBRZ LDA TWELVE
BRZ ERR
LDA NEG
BRZ ERR
LDA ZERO
BRZ TESTBRP
BRA ERR

# Test BRP
TESTBRP LDA NEG
BRP ERR
LDA TWELVE
BRP NEXT
BRA ERR
NEXT LDA ZERO
BRP TESTHLT
BRA ERR

# Test HLT
TESTHLT HLT
BRA ERR

# Error occurred
ERR LDA ERRNUM
OUT
HLT

# Data
ZERO DAT
NEG DAT -1
TWELVE DAT 12
TWENTY DAT 20
THIRTYTWO DAT 32
EIGHT DAT 8
PLACE DAT
ERRNUM DAT -1